-- 2010-11-23T18:53:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-23/mccourts-become-officially-divorced-with-dodgers-ownership-still-undecided.html
Los Angeles Dodgers owner Frank
McCourt and his wife were officially divorced, leaving the issue
of who owns the Major League Baseball team still to be decided
by a court in California.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Edvard Pettersson in Los Angeles at 
